OL,3,CStarmer: 'Difficult questions' over
OL,4,Cpolice handling of Henry Nowak's murder
OL,6,FThe prime minister vowed to "right the
OL,7,Fwrongs" in the Henry Nowak case after
OL,8,Fmeeting his family
OL,10,FSir Keir Starmer has said "difficult
OL,11,Fquestions" must be answered over the
OL,12,Fpolice handling of Henry Nowak's
OL,13,Fmurder, as he vowed to "right the
OL,14,Fwrongs" after meeting his family.
OL,16,FThe prime minister met with the family
OL,17,Fof the 18-year-old Southampton
OL,18,Fstudent, whose treatment by police has
OL,19,Fsparked a political row, at Downing
OL,20,FStreet on Thursday.
OL,26,@rD@[OUsD@JO]uD@XOUvD@GO]
