OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780661502
OL,3,CStarmer: 'Difficult questions' over
OL,4,Cpolice handling of Henry Nowak's murder
OL,6,FFollowing the meeting, Starmer paid
OL,7,Ftribute to Mr Nowak, saying he
OL,8,F"deserves a legacy that goes beyond
OL,9,Fthis awful tragedy".
OL,11,F"I was moved to learn more about Henry
OL,12,F` his kindness, his warmth, and his
OL,13,Flove of football ` and am grateful to
OL,14,Fhis family," he said.
OL,16,F"There is no doubt he had a bright
OL,17,Ffuture ahead of him, a future cruelly
OL,18,Fstolen from him in appalling
OL,19,Fcircumstances."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
