CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780661502
OL,3,CStarmer: 'Difficult questions' over
OL,4,Cpolice handling of Henry Nowak's murder
OL,6,FThere has been widespread outrage
OL,7,Fafter police bodycam footage showed
OL,8,Fofficers putting Mr Nowak in handcuffs
OL,9,Fas he lay dying, after his killer,
OL,10,FVickrum Digwa, claimed he had been the
OL,11,Fvictim of a racial attack.
OL,13,FPolice ignored his repeated pleas that
OL,14,Fhe could not breathe.
OL,16,FDigwa has been given a life sentence
OL,17,Fwith a minimum of 21 years in prison
OL,18,Ffor stabbing Mr Nowak with a
OL,19,Fceremonial knife with a 21cm blade,
OL,20,Fwhich he carried as part of his Sikh
OL,21,Freligion.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780661502
OL,3,CStarmer: 'Difficult questions' over
OL,4,Cpolice handling of Henry Nowak's murder
OL,6,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,7,FConduct (IOPC) said its independent
OL,8,Finvestigation "remains ongoing".
OL,10,FAfter meeting Mr Nowak's mother,
OL,11,Ffather and stepmother, Starmer said:
OL,12,F"We will be unflinching in taking
OL,13,Fwhatever action is required to right
OL,14,Fthe wrongs in this case.
OL,16,F"It is our duty now to ensure that
OL,17,Flessons are learned, that justice is
OL,18,Fdelivered and that we choose unity and
OL,19,Fprogress over division and hatred.
OL,20,FThis is the only way to honour Henry's
OL,21,Fmemory."
OL,26,@xD@AOU}D@HO]
