CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780661502
OL,3,CStarmer: 'Difficult questions' over
OL,4,Cpolice handling of Henry Nowak's murder
OL,6,FThe prime minister has already urged
OL,7,Fpoliticians to heed the teenager's
OL,8,Frelatives' calls not to use the case
OL,9,F"to cause disturbances" and branded
OL,10,FNigel Farage's response "unforgivable".
OL,12,FThe Reform leader hit back at the
OL,13,Fcriticism, insisting he condemns "all
OL,14,Fviolence" and has agreed to meet Mr
OL,15,FNowak's family.
OL,17,FThis is a breaking story, more to
OL,18,Ffollow
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@WO]rD@YOUrD@fO]uD@bOUvD@IO]
